um, row count, validation status, and final product_master reconciliation. Feed these fields into the RAG knowledge base so future AutoRCA can distinguish data defects, platform defects, and SLA defects without relying on a single log line.",Y,328,86,3.81,,,pandas_to_sql_append,10000,3,duplicate_product_id_load,INC002|INC025,8GB,4GB,32MB,N,,
