ter reconciliation. Feed these fields into the RAG knowledge base so future AutoRCA can distinguish data defects, platform defects, and SLA defects without relying on a single log line.",Y,328,19,17.26,,,postgres_copy_staging,50000,3,identifier_type_mismatch,INC004|INC026,8GB,4GB,32MB,N,,
